	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm sorry, Ainarki is right, rude as heck but right. The item needed for these sleaves are off level 60 mobs in Temple of Veeshan. I'm not sure a comment about a level 55+ item by a level 40 monk about being hit by level 50 mobs makes sense here. Once your closer to 55+ you will agree with him. AC is important, Agil and Dex are much less important. Resists are handy as well but levels resist more then resists do. Levels also help you keep from getting hit, that is if the level is to your advantage.<br><br>Symoril Thar'daan, Phantasmist<br>Szirax Szithisar, Master<br>Cerulean Stormcast, Evoker<br>Mercenary Force<br>Innoruuk<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
